  "payload_json": "{\"format_version\":\"1.0\",\"metadata\":{\"id\":\"config\",\"name\":\"vector-index-tuning\",\"version\":\"0.1.0\",\"description\":\"Optimize QMD vector search for better retrieval accuracy\",\"tags\":[\"qmd\",\"search\",\"optimization\",\"memory\"],\"requires\":[],\"provides\":[],\"platforms\":[],\"author\":null,\"license\":null},\"sections\":[{\"id\":\"overview\",\"title\":\"Overview\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"overview-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"Optimize our QMD (QMD) search system for better retrieval. Our current setup uses hash embeddings + BM25 hybrid. This skill provides tuning strategies.\"}]},{\"id\":\"current-setup\",\"title\":\"Current Setup\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"current-setup-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```\\nCollections:\\n- notes: 61 files (Brain notes)\\n- transcripts: 34 files\\n- memory: 4 files (daily memory)\\n- main, longterm, brain, brain-notes (empty)\\n```\"}]},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies\",\"title\":\"Tuning Strategies\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"### 1. Chunk Size Optimization\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-2\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Problem:** Too small = lose context. Too large = noisy.\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-3\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Current:** Default QMD chunking\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-4\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Tune:** Adjust chunk size in qmd config:\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-5\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```bash\\nqmd config --set chunk_size 512  # or 1024, 2048\\n```\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-6\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"### 2. Re-ranking Configuration\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-7\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Problem:** BM25 + embeddings may rank differently.\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-8\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Current:** RRF (Reciprocal Rank Fusion) combining both\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-9\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Tune:** Adjust weights in config:\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-10\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```toml\\n[search]\\nbm25_weight = 0.6    # increase for keyword precision\\nembedding_weight = 0.4  # increase for semantic recall\\n```\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-11\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"### 3. Collection-Specific Tuning\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-12\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Notes (technical content):**\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-13\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```toml\\n[search]\\nbm25_weight = 0.7   # more keyword matching\\nmin_score = 0.01\\n```\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-14\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"**Memory (conversational):**\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-15\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```toml\\n[search]\\nbm25_weight = 0.4   # more semantic\\nembedding_weight = 0.6\\n```\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-16\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"### 4. Re-index Trigger\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-17\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"When to rebuild index:\\n- After bulk imports (50+ new files)\\n- When search quality degrades\\n- Monthly maintenance\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-18\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```bash\\n### 5. Hybrid Search Tuning\\n\\n**Current command:**\\n```bash\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-19\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"qmd hybrid \\\"query\\\"\"},{\"id\":\"tuning-strategies-block-20\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```\\n\\n**Better queries:**\\n```bash\"}]},{\"id\":\"diagnostics\",\"title\":\"Diagnostics\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"diagnostics-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"### Check Index Health\"}]},{\"id\":\"our-specific-config\",\"title\":\"Our Specific Config\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"our-specific-config-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```bash\\n### Identify Issues\\n\\n| Symptom | Likely Cause | Fix |\\n|---------|--------------|-----|\\n| No results for common terms | BM25 not indexed | `qmd collection add` |\\n| Irrelevant results | Weight imbalance | Adjust weights |\\n| Missing recent items | Embeddings stale | `qmd embed -c <collection>` |\\n| Slow searches | Too many files | Chunk larger |\\n\\n\\nCurrent `.config/ms/config.toml`:\\n```toml\"},{\"id\":\"our-specific-config-block-2\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"[search]\\nbm25_weight = 0.5\\nembedding_backend = \\\"hash\\\"  # fast, deterministic\\nembedding_dims = 384\\nsemantic_weight = 0.5\\nuse_embeddings = true\"}]},{\"id\":\"optimization-plan\",\"title\":\"Optimization Plan\",\"blocks\":[]},{\"id\":\"commands-reference\",\"title\":\"Commands Reference\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"commands-reference-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"code\",\"content\":\"```\\n\\n\\n1. **Weekly:** Re-embed collections\\n2. **Monthly:** Tune weights based on query success\\n3. **Quarterly:** Review chunk sizes\\n\\n\\n```bash\"}]},{\"id\":\"current-known-issues\",\"title\":\"Current Known Issues\",\"blocks\":[{\"id\":\"current-known-issues-block-1\",\"block_type\":\"text\",\"content\":\"- `qmd query` and `qmd vsearch` try to download embedding model (1.2GB) which may fail\\n- **Workaround:** Use `qmd search` for BM25-only which works reliably\\n- Our current setup: hash embeddings (fast) + BM25 (reliable)\"}]}]}",
